msgid "Checking the integrity of the download and storage device..."
msgstr "Kontrollitakse allalaadimise ja salvestusseadme terviklikkust..."
msgid "Outdated Version"
msgstr "Aegunud versioon"
msgid ""
"Do you want to proceed with the installation of this old version anyway? BigLinux is a system with "
"weekly updates and this version was released more than a month ago. We recommend downloading a more "
"recent version."
msgstr ""
"Kas soovite ikkagi selle vana versiooni installimisega jätkata? BigLinux on süsteem, millel on "
"iganädalased uuendused ja see versioon ilmus rohkem kui kuu aega tagasi. Soovitame alla laadida "
"uuema versiooni."
